From: Harrison Ju <harrisonju@gmail.com>
Date: Sat, 7 Mar 2026 03:24:52 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 4/6] feat(zed): auto-discover PrisM models from /v1/models

On auth success, fetch GET /v1/models and populate the model selector
from PrisM's live catalog. Settings-configured models override fetched
entries by name. Fetch fails silently if PrisM is unreachable.

Also fixes Anthropic provider to surface tool_use content blocks as
OpenAI-format tool_calls in non-streaming responses.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
